{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/upload-svg-files-to-wordpress/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Allowing SVG Files in WordPress so you can upload them through the Media panel is surprisingly simple. This allows you to harness the power and speed benefits of SVG Files as opposed to Raster Images.</p>\n<p>Either add the following snippet to your theme's <code>functions.php</code> file or create a WordPress plugin that executes the following code:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">harnerdesigns_mime_types</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$mimes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token variable\">$mimes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'svg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'image/svg+xml'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$mimes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">add_filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'upload_mimes'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'harnerdesigns_mime_types'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>There are <a href=\"https://security.stackexchange.com/questions/11384/exploits-or-other-security-risks-with-svg-upload\">security concerns</a> to allowing SVG files to be uploaded, so make sure that only trusted contributors have access to uploading.</p>","excerpt":"Allowing SVG Files in WordPress so you can upload them through the Media panel is surprisingly simple. This allows you to harness the power and speed…","wordCount":{"words":77},"frontmatter":{"date":"November 28, 2018","updated":null,"title":"Upload SVG Files To WordPress","subtitle":"","tags":["WordPress"],"featuredImage":{"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/jackharner-gatsby/jackharner-gatsby/content/blog/upload-svg-files-to-wordpress/featuredImage.png","childImageSharp":{"original":{"src":"/static/featuredImage-124be52bbf346d8c60c354150e3cbdd7.png"}}},"ogImage":null},"fields":{"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »","slug":"/blog/upload-svg-files-to-wordpress/","ogImage":"","date":"November 28, 2018","unlisted":false}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/upload-svg-files-to-wordpress/","related":[{"id":"0c886846-cb1e-543e-8d0a-c79c0f6ecf77","excerpt":"JackHarner.com is built with Gatsby, a framework based on React that makes blazing fast websites. Gatsby Logo I have my Blog and Portfolio…","fields":{"date":"2019-12-22T18:23:53.017Z","slug":"/blog/auto-generate-content-gatsby/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Auto-Generate Content Folders In Gatsby","subtitle":"Preformat Your Frontmatter & More","tags":["Gatsby","Node","Automation"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/bc2a937d47ea91cb852001a44e11cff7/5ff92/featuredImage.jpg"}}}}},{"id":"764ccb3a-e431-5f64-b01c-62a44d492656","excerpt":"I'm Lazy. BUT I'm the good kind of lazy that works really hard to do as little actual work as possible. If I have to do anything more than…","fields":{"date":"2020-07-01T01:13:41.217Z","slug":"/blog/productivity-equals-automation/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{